<button class="d-module-header__icon" data-open="moduleShare" aria-label="Share">
  <%= external_icon "icons/solid/share-square.svg", role: "img", "aria-hidden": true %>
</button>

<button class="d-module-header__icon" data-open="moduleInfo" aria-label="More information">
  <%= external_icon "icons/solid/info-circle.svg", role: "img", "aria-hidden": true %>
</button>

<div class="reveal" id="moduleShare" data-reveal>
  <div class="reveal__header">
    <h3 class="reveal__title">Compartir:</h3>
    <button class="close-button" data-close aria-label="Close modal" type="button">
      <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
    </button>
  </div>
  <div class="button-group text-center">
    <a class="button button--twitter">
      <%= icon "twitter" %>
    </a>
    <a class="button button--facebook">
      <%= icon "facebook" %>
    </a>
    <a class="button button--google">
      <%= icon "google" %>
    </a>
    <a class="button secondary">
      <%= icon "github" %>
    </a>
    <a class="button secondary">
      <%= icon "instagram" %>
    </a>
    <a class="button secondary" data-open="urlShare">
      <%= icon "link-intact" %>
    </a>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="reveal" id="urlShare" data-reveal>
  <div class="reveal__header">
    <h3 class="reveal__title">Compartir enlace:</h3>
    <button class="close-button" data-close aria-label="Close modal" type="button">
      <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
    </button>
  </div>
  <h4 class="heading4">https://decidim.barcelona/thislinkinparticular</h4>
</div>


<div class="reveal" id="moduleInfo" data-reveal>
  <div class="reveal__header">
    <h3 class="reveal__title">About processes</h3>
    <button class="close-button" data-close aria-label="Close modal" type="button">
      <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
    </button>
  </div>
  <div>
    <p>A través de les Sessions Informatives organitzades als 6 Centres Cívics de la ciutat s’explicarà el procés en general, els moments de participació de la ciutadania i d’altres aspectes clau per a una correcta participació</p>
  </div>
</div>